Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.12,0:22:58.78,A_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs32\pos(960,980)}わたし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.12,0:22:58.78,A_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs32\pos(1066,980)}ささ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:13.56,A_JP,,0,0,0,,青い炎はふたり出会うための灯
