Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:35.92,A_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs32\pos(907,980)}さいご
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:35.92,A_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs32\pos(1040,980)}わたし
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:35.92,A_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs32\pos(1146,980)}うで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:35.92,A_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs32\pos(1253,980)}なか
